graph TD
    %% UI Layer
    A[UI Layer] -->|React| B[Web Application]
    A -->|React Native| C[Mobile Application]

    %% API Layer
    B -->|REST API| D[API Gateway]
    C -->|REST API| D

    %% Services Layer
    D -->|Node.js| E[Authentication Service]
    D -->|Node.js| F[Data Processing Service]
    D -->|Node.js| G[Notification Service]
    D -->|Node.js| H[Reporting Service]

